{"tid":588563,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我想quit u","createTime":"2018-03-11T09:53:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-18T11:13:50.000Z","uid":81282,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3b71fe1745f500f1f979c6d69f10206420088896","tid":588563,"uid":81282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T09:53:20.000Z","msg":"讀到year 3，呢三年都唔知自己讀左啲咩，GPA未試過過3，最高拎過一次A，仲要係有人carry，其他唔係B- 就C+ <br />\n呢兩個sem成日唔番學，科科都跟唔上，功課唔想做，上堂唔聽書，我覺得自己好廢，望住其他同學埋頭抄緊notes 我唔知係到做緊乜咁，聽都聽唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實由DSE完去In呢一科果陣我已經無興趣，一聽個名就已經唔想讀，只係諗住睇下佢收先算，由開始到而家都對呢科野一啲興趣都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但一開始又唔夠GPA tran major，愈讀愈唔想讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其他同學好多都諗好左自己條路要點行，但我真係諗唔到，覺得自己好廢，但又無勇氣quit，quit完又唔知可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 求屌醒"},{"pid":"0e7e080d8e00c97f95f640343cf0b80e4d8013cd","tid":588563,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T09:59:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"99161b737371ca056cd0a68a874da79aaef40de1","tid":588563,"uid":127952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T10:41:53.000Z","msg":"咩u先？"},{"pid":"a6d5aaf99dc6c2550b91f90dff151e79ab5ea398","tid":588563,"uid":3500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T10:45:56.000Z","msg":"咩科咩u<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58b5c424d3459de7400ca979d98caa4647dc7aaa","tid":588563,"uid":34321,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T10:47:39.000Z","msg":"唔好quit，涯多兩年有u grad 搵嘢做方便好多<br />\ntran 唔到就搵啲自己有興趣既科讀吓，有無想學既語文?<br />\n大學係最自由既時間，讀書唔係全部，行咗兩年幾無謂又quit u 重新讀過<br />\n<br />\n當年year 1 gpa &lt;1.5，又係無興趣加GPA唔好轉唔到，最後third hon"},{"pid":"179412d4854f4f09da075c8df6b7dbd5aa5b201e","tid":588563,"uid":51250,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T10:49:19.000Z","msg":"差1年咪讀埋佢<br />\n點都多一個degree<br />\n畀多啲選擇自己"},{"pid":"e7f124f9acb9806c0ec20d6f0a1a60f47858229b","tid":588563,"uid":90841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T10:49:43.000Z","msg":"加油呀 u are not a窿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都係year3 gpa得2點0幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n讀咁耐淨係攞過1支A (仲要唔係自己major)<br />\n曾好想好想轉major <br />\n因為又唔係讀咩專業科<br />\n連第時搵工都有困難<br />\n<br />\n不過讀書都係人生既其中一個過程啫<br />\n今日讀唔掂 唔代表出到黎做野都唔掂嘛<br />\n雖然唔知第時可以點<br />\n但係盡力做好眼前既事就起碼唔會後悔嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n加油呀!!"},{"pid":"85923ba087116df4caaefb85e258742e17330c7e","tid":588563,"uid":34444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T10:58:50.000Z","msg":"Quit la"},{"pid":"4f57580bfd23680478979844037723c55acdef47","tid":588563,"uid":81282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e7e080d8e00c97f95f640343cf0b80e4d8013cd","tid":588563,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T09:59:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T02:08:53.000Z","msg":"無家底<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98c50dddc7cb8d043d945733dc870e61b213a9ea","tid":588563,"uid":81282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6d5aaf99dc6c2550b91f90dff151e79ab5ea398","tid":588563,"uid":3500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T10:45:56.000Z","msg":"咩科咩u<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T02:09:35.000Z","msg":"乞食科，係8大入面唔出面既U<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"388f997532c1dbc0d90c114ffce4609aea28